561
00:35:08,260 --> 00:35:09,700
(By the time I could remember things,)

562
00:35:10,620 --> 00:35:12,940
(there was only one cherry tree
left in the garden,)

563
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:14,860
(and one plum tree.)

564
00:35:15,740 --> 00:35:19,100
(Because neither of them bore much fruit.)

565
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,511
Order of the Mountain Ghost.

566
