Are you okay?

590
00:36:51,900 --> 00:36:52,660
I'm fine.

591
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,700
What's going on with
Order of the Mountain Ghost?

592
00:36:55,700 --> 00:36:56,460
Tell me about it.

593
00:36:56,620 --> 00:36:58,111
What kind of person is the author?

594
00:36:58,740 --> 00:36:59,860
The author

595
00:37:00,266 --> 00:37:01,420
