596
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:02,460
A new author.

597
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:03,580
He writes day and night.

598
00:37:03,580 --> 00:37:04,400
He works really hard.

599
00:37:04,555 --> 00:37:05,660
But still not as good as you.

600
00:37:13,622 --> 00:37:16,490
Ms. Lin, everyone knows the company is
promoting Order of the Mountain Ghost,

601
00:37:16,500 --> 00:37:18,200
so naturally,
they have feelings about it.

602
00:37:18,420 --> 00:37:19,580
Naobaijin has always wanted

603
