How long has it been
since you last wrote with a pen?

622
00:38:13,460 --> 00:38:14,500
Quite a while.

623
00:38:14,777 --> 00:38:15,911
I realized something.

624
00:38:15,977 --> 00:38:17,222
Writing isn't like driving.

625
00:38:17,288 --> 00:38:19,420
Even if you haven't been driving
for ten years,

626
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:21,250
