686
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,700
If we run into each other,

687
00:41:39,700 --> 00:41:40,820
I would be really happy, too.

688
00:41:40,820 --> 00:41:43,066
And I'd love to hear
whatever you want to share.

689
